IMAPStore personal-remote
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
UserCmd "~/.config/neomutt/secrets/get-personal-user"
PassCmd "~/.config/neomutt/secrets/get-personal-pass"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType NONE
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.config/neomutt/mails/Personal/
Inbox ~/.config/neomutt/mails/Personal/Inbox

Channel personal 
Expunge Both
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

IMAPStore work-remote 
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
UserCmd "~/.config/neomutt/secrets/get-work-user"
PassCmd "~/.config/neomutt/secrets/get-work-key"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore work-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.config/neomutt/mails/Work/
Inbox ~/.config/neomutt/mails/Work/Inbox

Channel work
Expunge both
Far :work-remote:
Near :work-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile
